  "task": "# Relay stage 1: Ideate\nTask: disable-new-buttons-when-project-isn-t-selected\nWorking directory: /Users/admin/Dev/temp-visual-relay/\n\n## Task input\n# Disable New Buttons When Project Isn't Selected\n\nI was able to create a new LLM task when no project was selected. The \"New\" button should be disabled if no project folder has been selected.\n\n## Manifest\n(not set yet)\n\n## Task context\n### Screenshot 2026-06-30 at 2.50.53\u202fPM.png (188322 bytes, not inlined)\n\n## Prior stages\n\n\nEnd your reply with a single fenced ```json block, nothing after it, matching: { \"summary\": string, \"options\": string[] }",
